Package clinic.src.project

Class Provider

java.lang.Object
clinic.src.project.Person
clinic.src.project.Provider
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Person>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Doctor, Technician
public abstract class Provider extends Person
Provider class is an abstract class that represents a provider in the system. It's a superclass to represent either a doctor or a technician, while being a subclass of person.
